collectible.name: The Lost Gnomes Lamp
collectible.description:
When new Scarcity residents got to the island, they started finding hints of a lost gnome civilization, but no sights of gnomes themselves. What happened to them?

This lamp should aid in looking for discoveries throughout the winter.

1 lamp will be airdropped to each current resident, with a small reserve left for new residents or awards. 7.5% of secondary sales go towards planting trees in the real world! Let's see how many we can plant in the new year.

~ Happy Solstice 2021! ~
collectible.author: 0xb7d3a787a39f25457ca511dc3f0591b546f5e02f

collectible.name: Modern Gnome Art - "Múrien"
collectible.description:
This murky lavender and turquoise painting's english name is "Monday" but the gnomish means "sleep or dreams", part of Water faction.

Our artifacts research lab determined the artist of this 7 piece day of the week series to be a middle-class gnome by the name of Celxi Pebblestamp (currently unknown whereabouts), but we do know that she loved color!

This piece could fetch a pretty penny to a collector who wants more than one.

Also for a limited time, owners of this piece who sign the guestbook in Silver Town Hall will receive an airdropped statue of the Scarcity lantern lady in their unique colorway.

After distributing to active 1st and/or 2nd parcel owners, extra copies of this NFT *might* be burned.

collectible.description: When ye need to mine for somethin' rare n' fine, pick dig n' pick, losin' track of yer time...

collectible.name: Basic Gnome Hat of the Water Faction
collectible.description: It's raining hats! If you've received this Scarcity airdrop, it means the discovery you presented was linked to a certain gnome faction determined by its color or properties. You can team up with others in your faction to create new lore, improved hats, other faction items, themed art shows, contests, or other events! Extra hats will be available for purchase if you'd like to switch factions or invite a friend to the story who doesn't own land. All proceeds will go to planting real life trees.
collectible.author: 0xb7d3a787a39f25457ca511dc3f0591b546f5e02f

collectible.name: Scarcity Coin - Silver
collectible.description: The little gnome is yelling "wen coin"! Well a treasure trove of these 1024 coins were found in a Silver suburb commons. They will be distributed evenly amongst Silver residents and the discoverer, with a Jan 1 2022 snapshot. What happens with them next is up to you.
collectible.author: 0xb7d3a787a39f25457ca511dc3f0591b546f5e02f

collectible.name: Shovel of the Air Faction
collectible.description:
You found a Scarcity working class gnome's shovel with a handle in the colors of Air.

Researchers say it's a common item for mining, gardening, displaying attendance somewhere, or even as an emergency weapon. It still looks good to carry, or you may be able to craft it into something else as the metal, wood, and Air gem handle appear to be in decent shape!

After copies are distributed to an active 1st and/or 2nd owner, the remaining quantity of this NFT might be burned.
